  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <div type="mūlam" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV20">
<l>alarperi teṉṟalu mayalvarai vuraittalu</l>
<l>mulakiyal kūṟiya nīyurai yeṉṟaluñ</l>
<l>curañcela vāṟṟu niṉṉō ṭeṉṟalum</l>
<l>varuntiṟa muraittalum vaḻinayap pittalum</l>
<l>virumpiṉa ṉērnta pāvak kiḷaviyum</l>
<l>poruntu meṉmaṉār pōkkuṭaṉ valittal.</l></lg>
</div>
</body>
</text>
<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <head xml:lang="en">Commentary</head>
      <p xml:id="TNV20comm1">eṉpatu uṭaṉ pōkku valittal ām āṟuṇarttutaṉutaliṟṟu.</p>
      <p xml:lang="en">The quoted [<hi rend="italic">cūttiram</hi>] intends to make known the way in which 'encouraging elopement' occurs.</p>
     <p xml:id="TNV20comm2">alar periteṉṟaṉ mutal ākak kiḷavi yīṟākac collap paṭṭa kiḷavikaḷai 
     yuṭaitteṉṟu colluvar uṭaṉ pōkku valittalai eṉṟa vāṟu.</p> 
     <p xml:lang="en">They say about 'ecouraging elopement' that it possesses those aforementioned speech situations, beginning with 'talking about the gossip being great' and ending with 'the speech of pity'.</p>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV20poem1"> 
        <l>nilavō raṉṉa veṇmaṇaṟ pākkattu</l>
        <l>malarēr kūntaṉ maṭantaik</l>
        <l>kalarā kiṉṟā laṇṇaṉiṉ ṉaruḷē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV20koḷu1">eṉpatu muṉ ṉiṉṟalar periteṉṟatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV20poem2"> 
        <l>aṇikoṇarn taṉarē yayalō raṇṇal</l>
        <l>tuṇivuṟu ceyti yātukoṉ</l>
        <l>maṇipurai kūntaṉ maṭantaitaṉ vayiṉē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV20koḷu2">eṉpatu ayal varaivuraittatu.</p>
</div> 
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV20poem3"> 
        <l>paṉināṭ ṭāmarai pōlap paiyat</l>
        <l>tuṉiyā kiṉṟā ṉeñca melliyaṉ</l>
        <l>miṉcēr nuṇṇiṭai tiṟattiṉi</l>
        <l>yeṉceyaṟ pāla vilaṅkiḻai tāmē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV20koḷu3">eṉpatu tōḻiyait talaimakaṉ viṉāyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV20poem4"> 
        <l>yāṉeva ṉaṟikō vaṇṇal vāṉoṭu</l>
        <l>nāṉila muḻutum peṟiṉum</l>
        <l>pēṇā rammavivaḷ pūṇiḷa mulaikkē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV20koḷu4">eṉpatu yāṉ aṟiyēṉī yurai yeṉṟatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV20poem5"> 
        <l>tīya veyya veṉkuvai yāyiṉ</l>
        <l>yāvatu miṉiya kāṉañ</l>
        <l>cēyuyar cilampa niṉṉoṭu celiṉē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV20koḷu5">eṉpatu curañcela vāṟṟuniṉṉōṭeṉṟatu.</p>
</div>  
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV20poem6"> 
        <l>tērum piṟavu nīkki yillayal</l>
        <l>yāvarum payilā voruciṟai</l>
        <l>vārpūñ cilampa varutaṉiṉ kaṭaṉē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV20koḷu6">eṉpatu varun tiṟamoḻintatu.</p>
</div>  
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV20poem7"> 
        <l>uḷaruñ<!--note place="foot">We can make good sense of this reading and I believe that the editor/scribe who made the paper copy may have mistaken <p xml:lang="ta">uḷa</p> for <p xml:lang="ta">ū</p> as the two look similar.</note--> cēriyu malareḻa yāyun</l>
        <l>tāṉē yirukka taṉmaṉai yāṉē</l>
        <l>tiruntuvēl viṭalaiyoṭu keḻīi</l>
        <l>yaruñcurañ cēṟal purintaṉa ṉiṉiyē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV20koḷu7">eṉpatu uṭaṉ pōkku nayappittatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV20poem8"> 
        <l>kāṉaṅ kārpeyat taṇṇeṉ ṟaṉṟē</l>
        <l>vāṉa matiyu nāṇilā vutavu</l>
        <l>maṉṉai tuyaramu niṉṉaiyar vekuḷiyun</l>
        <l>taṇikkuvaṉ maṉṉō yāṉē</l>
        <l>maṇikkuḻaṉ mātaraik kāṇayāṉ maṟuttē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV20koḷu8">ituvum atu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV20poem9" corresp="#KT149"> 
        <l>aḷitō tāṉē nāṇē nammoṭu</l>
        <l>naṉinī ṭuḻantaṉṟu maṉṉē yiṉiyē</l>
        <l>vāṉpūṅ karumpi ṉōṅkumaṇaṟ ciṟuciṟait</l>
        <l>tīmpuṉa ṉērtara vīntuk kāṅkut</l>
        <l>tāṅku maḷavait tāṅkik</l>
        <l>kāma neritarak kainnil lātē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV20koḷu9">talaimakaḷ uṭaṉcela nērnta pāvakkiḷavi.<note> 20.</note></p>
</div>
<div><p xml:id="TNV20comm3">kaḷavu muṟṟum.</p></div>
</body>
